{"type":"message","id":"785f8735","parentId":"ecee704e","timestamp":"2026-05-29T11:15:49.842Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 完成！\n\n**已修复**：\n\n1. **设备配置文件**：`data/device_config.json` - 存储当前设备、历史设备\n2. **三个脚本独立运行入口**：\n   - `python -m src.advanced.function --ip 192.168.5.72`\n   - `python -m src.advanced.limit --ip 192.168.5.72`\n   - `python -m src.advanced.speed --ip 192.168.5.72`\n3. **设备管理脚本**：`python device.py`\n   - `device.py discover` - SADP发现\n   - `device.py scan 192.168.1.1-254` - ISAPI扫描\n   - `device.py add 192.168.5.72` - 添加设备\n   - `device.py modify <MAC> <新IP>` - 修改IP\n   - `device.py list` - 显示历史设备\n   - `device.py use <MAC>` - 设置当前设备\n\n**使用流程**：\n```\n1. device.py add 192.168.5.72 --password <密码>  # 添加设备\n2. device.py use <MAC>                           # 设置当前设备\n3. python -m src.advanced.function              # 运行测试（自动读取当前设备）\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":69502,"output":285,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69787,"cost":{"input":0.069502,"output":0.000912,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07041399999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780053335419,"responseId":"cht000d85c3@dx19e73725e19b8aa822"}}
{"type":"message","id":"27bea675","parentId":"785f8735","timestamp":"2026-05-29T11:16:00.903Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"29432\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-29 19:15 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\nFunction limit speed需要读取当前活跃设备，也就是astrohub设备已经连接的设备，同一个主机可能多开程序，可能同网络有多个设备，一个程序实例同一时间只能连接1个设备，这个设备就是激活设备\n做好设计，保证刚才说的各种需要，设计好复用和继承关系，实现这个功能，禁止过度开发"}],"timestamp":1780053360899}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8a5bc03","parentId":"27bea675","timestamp":"2026-05-29T11:16:10.140Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"理解需求：\n\n**核心设计**：\n- 一个程序实例 = 一个活跃设备\n- 活跃设备存储在 `device_config.json` 的 `current_device`\n- 所有测试脚本自动读取活跃设备\n\n**检查现有代码**："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7e40dc8e73034e47898bb432","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"astrohub/src/advanced/device_config.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":70019,"output":66,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70085,"cost":{"input":0.070019,"output":0.0002112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07023019999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780053360903,"responseId":"cht000de1b7@dx19e7372c32fb828282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecde1a39","parentId":"e8a5bc03","timestamp":"2026-05-29T11:16:10.147Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7e40dc8e73034e47898bb432","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v2.0 - 设备配置管理\n\n统一管理设备配置：\n- 读取/写入 device_config.json\n- 当前设备、历史设备\n- IP/MAC/型号等信息\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nCONFIG_FILE = Path(__file__).parent.parent.parent / \"data\" / \"device_config.json\"\n\n\ndef ensure_config() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"确保配置文件存在。\"\"\"\n    CONFIG_FILE.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    if not CONFIG_FILE.exists():\n        save_config({\n            \"current_device\": None,\n            \"devices\": {}\n        })\n    return CONFIG_FILE\n\n\ndef load_config() -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"加载设备配置。\"\"\"\n    ensure_config()\n    with open(CONFIG_FILE, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        return json.load(f)\n\n\ndef save_config(config: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    \"\"\"保存设备配置。\"\"\"\n    CONFIG_FILE.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with open(CONFIG_FILE, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\n\ndef get_current_device() -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"获取当前设备信息。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    current_mac = config.get(\"current_device\")\n    if not current_mac:\n        return None\n    return config.get(\"devices\", {}).get(current_mac)\n\n\ndef set_current_device(mac: str, ip: str = \"\", model: str = \"\", port: int = 80) -> None:\n    \"\"\"设置当前设备。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").lower()\n    \n    config[\"current_device\"] = mac_clean\n    if mac_clean not in config.get(\"devices\", {}):\n        config.setdefault(\"devices\", {})[mac_clean] = {}\n    \n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"mac\"] = mac_clean\n    if ip:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"ip\"] = ip\n    if model:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"model\"] = model\n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"port\"] = port\n    \n    save_config(config)\n\n\ndef update_device_info(mac: str, **kwargs) -> None:\n    \"\"\"更新设备信息。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").lower()\n    \n    if mac_clean not in config.get(\"devices\", {}):\n        config.setdefault(\"devices\", {})[mac_clean] = {\"mac\": mac_clean}\n    \n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean].update(kwargs)\n    save_config(config)\n\n\ndef list_devices() -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    \"\"\"列出所有历史设备。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    return list(config.get(\"devices\", {}).values())\n\n\ndef get_device_by_mac(mac: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"根据MAC获取设备信息。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").lower()\n    return config.get(\"devices\", {}).get(mac_clean)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780053370147}}
